mpressor er ofte kald, og en luftvarmer bør installeres i tillegg til trykkregulatoren og pustefilteret. Overtrykket leder sveiserøyk eller lakkstøv bort fra ansiktet.\",\"language\":\"nb\"},\"url\":\"https://api.test.ndla.no/concept-api/v1/drafts/4079\",\"contexts\":[],\"supportedLanguages\":[\"nb\",\"nn\"],\"learningResourceType\":\"concept\",\"status\":{\"current\":\"IN_PROGRESS\",\"other\":[\"PUBLISHED\"]},\"traits\":[],\"score\":0.0,\"highlights\":[{\"field\":\"users\",\"matches\":[\"<em>Gxfx7B-MXoFdgVZZ6p611C6w</em>\"]},{\"field\":\"learningResourceType\",\"matches\":[\"<em>concept</em>\"]}],\"paths\":[],\"lastUpdated\":\"2023-03-21T09:26:30.000Z\",\"license\":\"CC-BY-SA-4.0\",\"revisions\":[],\"responsible\":{\"responsibleId\":\"Gxfx7B-MXoFdgVZZ6p611C6w\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2023-03-21T08:37:20.000Z\"},\"favorited\":0,\"resultType\":\"concept\",\"typename\":\"MultiSearchSummaryDTO\"},{\"id\":4729,\"title\":{\"title\":\"hydraulisk energi\",\"htmlTitle\":\"hydraulisk energi\",\"language\":\"nb\"},\"metaDescription\":{\"metaDescription\":\"Hydraulisk energi er trykksatt væske i bevegelse, eksempelvis i et hydraulikkanlegg. test\",\"language\":\"nb\"},\"url\":\"https://api.test.ndla.no/concept-api/v1/drafts/4729\",\"contexts\":[],\"supportedLanguages\":[\"nb\"],\"learningResourceType\":\"concept\",\"status\":{\"current\":\"LANGUAGE\",\"other\":[]},\"traits\":[],\"score\":0.0,\"highlights\":[{\"field\":\"users\",\"matches\":[\"<em>Gxfx7B-MXoFdgVZZ6p611C6w</em>\"]},{\"field\":\"learningResourceType\",\"matches\":[\"<em>concept</em>\"]}],\"paths\":[],\"lastUpdated\":\"2023-03-20T14:15:58.000Z\",\"license\":\"CC-BY-SA-4.0\",\"revisions\":[],\"responsible\":{\"responsibleId\":\"Gxfx7B-MXoFdgVZZ6p611C6w\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2023-03-20T14:15:58.000Z\"},\"favorited\":0,\"resultType\":\"concept\",\"typename\":\"MultiSearchSummaryDTO\"},{\"id\":4889,\"title\":{\"title\":\"test bm 16.3\",\"htmlTitle\":\"test bm 16.3\",\"language\":\"nb\"},\"metaDescription\":{\"metaDescription